OL,6,FThe picture looked similar last year,
OL,7,Fwith 403 pharmacy closures across the
OL,8,Fcountry - a significant increase,
OL,9,Fhowever, compared to 2022, when 91
OL,10,Fclosed.
OL,12,FThe figures will come as a huge blow
OL,13,Fto ministers who launched their
OL,14,Fflagship Pharmacy First scheme, which
OL,15,Fgives pharmacists more powers to treat
OL,16,Fpatients for a number of conditions,
OL,17,Fwith the aim to ease pressure from GPs.
