OL,4,CEngland due to 'perfect storm'
OL,6,FNPA chief executive Paul Rees said:
OL,7,F"Community pharmacies face a perfect
OL,8,Fstorm of rapidly declining levels of
OL,9,Freal terms government funding and high
OL,10,Flevels of inflation, which is both
OL,11,Fincreasing the cost of dispensing
OL,12,Fmedicine and pushing many community
OL,13,Fpharmacies to the brink.
OL,15,F"Government funding no longer covers
OL,16,Fthe costs of the nation's medicines,
OL,17,Fleaving pharmacies to subsidise the
OL,18,FNHS from their own pockets.
