OL,6,FLouise Ansari, chief executive of
OL,7,FHealthwatch England, said: "The
OL,8,Fincrease in pharmacy closures in
OL,9,FEngland is concerning.
OL,11,F"People tell us what an essential
OL,12,Fsource pharmacies are for advice,
OL,13,Fdiagnosis and getting minor health
OL,14,Fissues treated. They also help in
OL,15,Freducing the pressure on GPs.
