OL,4,CEngland due to 'perfect storm'
OL,6,F"When a pharmacy closes, it impacts
OL,7,Fcommunities, especially older people
OL,8,Fwho are the most regular users and
OL,9,Fthose who don't have the means to
OL,10,Ftravel to a pharmacy that is further
OL,11,Faway.
OL,13,F"The pharmacy sector and healthcare
OL,14,Fsystem must work together to provide
OL,15,Fthe service people need."
OL,17,FDavid Fothergill, public health
OL,18,Fspokesperson for the Local Government
OL,19,FAssociation, added: "Pharmacies have
OL,20,Fan important place in our local
OL,21,Feconomy.
