OL,3,CTen pharmacies closing each week in
OL,4,CEngland due to 'perfect storm'
OL,6,F"They are vital to ensuring diverse
OL,7,Fand vibrant high streets, which can
OL,8,Fotherwise be dominated by betting
OL,9,Fshops, fast food outlets and coffee
OL,10,Fshops. Losing our pharmacies could
OL,11,Fleave gaps in high streets that may
OL,12,Fnever been filled."
OL,14,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "More than four in
OL,16,Ffive people live within a 20-minute
OL,17,Fwalk of a pharmacy, and there are
OL,18,Ftwice as many pharmacies in deprived
OL,19,Fareas, making access to care quicker
OL,20,Fand more convenient.
